Thank you for reading this file. Welcome to my project final based on a video game I have grown fond of and dedicated as much time to learning as I have this class. Thank you to my teacher and peers for helping me grow and come this far. I truly am grateful for all that you guys do and have done. Lets make this final project the best we got! 

Here you can find all my files and details about the recently revealed game MARATHON by Bungie. Originally created in 1994-1996, and continues it's legacy today in 2026 with the full release on March 5th of this year. I will detail a few things and create a page similar to what was once a message board in the early 2000's. I have grown along side the internet and intend to have a modern spin on what I have decided to write about. 
